OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another fine dry day
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine though high
OL,7,Fcloud may turn the sunshine hazy
OL,8,Flater. Very warm with some cooling sea
OL,9,Fbreezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA very warm and sunny evening
OL,12,Fwill be followed by a dry night with
OL,13,Fsome clear spells. Winds remaining
OL,14,Flight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother bright day with some
OL,17,Fsunshine a times and becoming hot away
OL,18,Ffrom sea breezes. Later there is a
OL,19,Fslight chance of some heavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
